org.framed.orm.model

Interface ModelElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, NamedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Relation, Shape
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ModelElementImpl, RelationImpl, ShapeImpl

    public interface ModelElement
extends NamedElement
    A representation of the model object 'Model Element'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Container
    • Incoming Relations
    • Outgoing Relations
    • Type

    See Also:
    OrmPackage.getModelElement()
